messages.messageBody:
************
http://www.freerice .com/index. php

This is a site where you earn rice by correctly answering vocabulary
questions; the rice is distributed to hungry people all over the world.
Each correct answer provides 10 grains of rice; I just donated 2000
:-)

The level of difficulty depends on your answers, so kids can play,
English learners can play, and those of us who are, well, wordy, can be
challenged, too.

Nancy

**************

Okay, that was totally addictive! I just spent 1/2 an hour doing that before I remembered I'm supposed to be doing something else <sheepishg>. Whoops. It has now been favorited to come back to later :-)
Thanks Nancy!



Meghan

messages.messageBody:
another point about this site is that you can get so absorbed discussing
words with your 17yo son that your jam boils over, all over the gas stove
top, down into the grill, and then you can have fun spending the next one
and a half hours cleaning the ******** thing!!

alternatively, you could do it at a time when you aren't in the middle of
making jam....

Cally
